The '''B'omarr Registry''' was a bound manuscript which kept record of the members of the [[B'omarr Order/Legends|B'omarr Order]] who achieved enlightenment. In addition to this, the thick registry contained a record of some of the monks' greatest philosophical musings. A copy of the Registry was known to be held in [[Shiin's Library]] in [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]].

